    "en": {
      "title": "A-level results are released",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Commissioner General of Examinations Mr. L. M. D. Dharmasena said that the results of the General Certificate of Education A Level 2021 examination were released this afternoon.",
        "The Commissioner General of Examinations also says that the examination results can be obtained through the websites www.doenets.lk and www.results.exams.gov.lk of the examination department.",
        "The Commissioner General of Examinations also stated that 236035 school applicants and 36647 private applicants appeared for this year's advanced level examination, totaling 272682 applicants."
      ],
